    ğŸ”¹ `--destdir directory` --> ğŸ¯ Specifies the destination directory for the generated `*.dwz` files. The default is `/usr/lib/debug/.dwz`.
    ğŸ”¹ `--name package-name` --> ğŸ·ï¸ Specifies the package name. If not specified, the source directory name is used.
    ğŸ”¹ `--compress-level level` --> ğŸ—œï¸ Specifies the compression level (from 1 to 9) for the `*.dwz` files. Higher compression levels result in smaller file sizes but longer compression times.
    ğŸ”¹ `--help` --> â“ Displays the command help.

ğŸ›  **Examples:**

    $ dh_dwz --sourcedir src --destdir deb/dwz
    
